title: American stars face stiff test from each other
text: > Top News American stars face stiff test from each other FILE - In this July 25, 2015, file photo, Gabby Douglas competes on the uneven bars during the Secret U.S. Classic gymnastics competition in Hoffman Estates, Ill. The U.S. women's gymnastics team should stroll through qualifying at the world championships on Saturday in Glascow, Scotland. Yet one of the three Americans who will compete in the all-around _ defending Olympic champion Gabby Douglas, two-time world champ Simone Biles or three-time Olympic medalist Aly Raisman _ will have to watch the all-around finals from the stands thanks to the rules that limit each country to two competitors in the finals. (AP Photo/Andrew A. Nelles, File)
